'''-{zh-hans:戴维·安东尼·安德鲁·阿梅斯; zh-hant:顏敏時; zh-hk:顏敏時}-'''爵士（{{lang-en|Sir David Anthony Andrew Amess}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|eɪ|m|ɪ|s}} {{respell|AY|miss}}，{{bd|1952年|3月26日|2021年|10月15日|catIdx=Amess}}），英国政治人物，[[保守党_(英国)|英国保守党]]党员，1983年起任[[国会议员_(英国)|英国国会议员]]，历任{{tsl|en|Basildon (UK Parliament constituency)|巴西尔登 (英国国会选区)|巴西尔登}}和[[西紹森德_(英國國會選區)|西紹森德]]两个选区议员。

埃默斯在[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]出生长大，在[[伯恩茅斯大学|伯恩茅斯大学]]修读经济与政府，毕业后当过一段时间[[小学|小学]]老师、承保从业员及招聘顾问。1982年，任[[紅橋區_(倫敦)|紅橋區]]保守党议员，1983年在英国议会选举中{{tsl|en|Bellwether#United Kingdom|头羊|一骑绝尘}}，拿下巴西尔登议席，体现“{{tsl|en|Essex man|埃塞克斯男人}}”对[[玛格丽特·撒切尔|玛格丽特·撒切尔]]政府的热忱。1992年成功获得连任，后因选区范围变动辞任，1997年任西绍森德选区议员，直至24年后遇害。

埃默斯在政府的最高职位是担任[[博文高|博文高]]{{tsl|en|Parliamentary Private Secretary|国会私人秘书}}12年，之后任[[后座议员|后座议员]]，在多个[[专责委员会_(英国)|专责委员会]]任职，支持多项法案，包括《防止残酷束缚法》（1988）和《家居供暖与节能法案》（2000），任内主张维护[[动物福利|动物福利]]、纪念[[拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格|拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格]]及支持[[子宮內膜異位症|子宮內膜異位症]]患者。

作为[[社会保守主义|社会保守主义]]派天主教徒，埃默斯{{tsl|en|Catholic Church and abortion|天主教会对堕胎的看法|反对堕胎}}和[[英国同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]。政治上支持{{tsl|en|Capital punishment in the United Kingdom|英国死刑制度|死刑}}和[[英国脱欧|脱欧]]。1983年结婚，有五个子女，二女为模特{{tsl|en|Katie Amess|凯蒂·埃默斯|凯蒂·埃-{}-默斯}}。

2021年10月15日，埃默斯在[[滨海利|滨海利]]主持“[[政治诊疗室|政治诊疗室]]”活动时，被人刺中数刀，当场死亡<ref name="Despite the best efforts of paramedics, sadly, he died at the scene.">{{Cite news|date=2021-10-15|title=MP David Amess dies after being stabbed at constituency meeting|work=The Guardian|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/15/mp-david-amess-dies-after-being-stabbed-at-constituency-surgery|access-date=2021-10-16|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017173718/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/15/mp-david-amess-dies-after-being-stabbed-at-constituency-surgery|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[索馬里人|索马里裔]]英国公民阿里·哈比·哈里涉嫌谋杀被捕，依照《[[2000年恐怖主义法令|2000年恐怖主义法令]]》被拘留。据称阿里信奉{{tsl|en|Islamic extremism|极端伊斯兰教}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/uk-mps-killer-was-referred-to-counter-terrorism-scheme-reports|title=British MP's killer was referred to counter-terrorism scheme: Reports|website=[[The_Straits_Times<!--_(Singapore)_-->|The Straits Times<!-- (Singapore) -->]]|date=2021-10-17|access-date=2021-10-17|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017193909/https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/uk-mps-killer-was-referred-to-counter-terrorism-scheme-reports|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==早年与职业生涯==
1952年3月26日，戴维·安东尼·安德鲁·埃默斯在[[埃塞克斯郡|埃塞克斯郡]]{{tsl|en|Plaistow, Essex|普拉斯托 (埃塞克斯郡)|普拉斯托}}的一个工人阶级家庭出生<ref name="Tele obit">{{Cite news|date=2021-10-15|title=Sir David Amess, well-liked, hard-working and robustly Right-wing Conservative MP for Basildon and then Southend West – obituary|work=The Telegraph|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2021/10/15/sir-david-amess-well-liked-hard-working-robustly-right-wing/|access-date=2021-10-17|subscription=yes|issn=0307-1235|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017175247/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/obituaries/2021/10/15/sir-david-amess-well-liked-hard-working-robustly-right-wing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父亲詹姆斯·埃默斯（James Amess）是电工，母亲莫德·马丁（Maud Martin）是裁缝<ref name="Times obit">{{Cite news|title=David Amess obituary: Brexiteer, animal rights campaigner and committed local MP|newspaper=The Times|date=2021-10-15|url=https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/david-amess-mp-qdjqr7sf9|access-date=2021-10-17|subscription=yes|issn=0140-0460|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017120759/https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/david-amess-mp-qdjqr7sf9|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Tele obit" /><ref>{{cite web |last=McGreevy |first=Ronan |title=Irish priest remembers David Amess as a man who took his faith seriously |url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/irish-priest-remembers-david-amess-as-a-man-who-took-his-faith-seriously-1.4702736 |website=The Irish Times |access-date=2021-10-17 |date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2021-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017110123/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/ireland/irish-news/irish-priest-remembers-david-amess-as-a-man-who-took-his-faith-seriously-1.4702736 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。母亲一样，埃默斯自小信奉[[天主教會|罗马天主教]]<ref name="newstate">{{cite web|url=https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/maud-amess-celebrates-104th-birthday|title=Maud Amess celebrates 104th Birthday|publisher=David Amess|date=2016-05-04|access-date=2019-01-08|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016085917/https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/maud-amess-celebrates-104th-birthday|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/14811812.mp-sir-david-amess-pays-tribute-to-inspirational-mum-who-has-died-aged-104/|title=MP Sir David Amess pays tribute to 'inspirational' mum, who has died aged 104|first=Robyn|last=Pierce|date=2016-10-20|access-date=2019-01-08|work=Echo|location=Basildon Canvey Southend|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016085916/https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/14811812.mp-sir-david-amess-pays-tribute-to-inspirational-mum-who-has-died-aged-104/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

埃默斯就读于圣安东尼小学和幼儿学校（St Anthony's Junior and Infant School）及[[森林門|森林門]]圣博纳旺德文法学校（今{{tsl|en|St Bonaventure's|圣博纳旺蒂尔}}天主教学校）<ref>{{Cite web|last=Shaw|first=Neil|date=2021-10-15|title=MP stabbed multiple times at constituency surgery|url=https://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/news/uk-world-news/mp-david-amess-stabbed-essex-6065918|access-date=2021-10-16|website=HullLive|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015135359/https://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/news/uk-world-news/mp-david-amess-stabbed-essex-6065918|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就读圣博纳旺德期间加入学生的革命党（Revolutionist Party），主张最低额度的零花钱及取消家庭作业<ref name="Guardian obit">{{cite web |last=Bates |first=Stephen |title=Sir David Amess obituary |url=https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2021/oct/17/sir-david-amess-obituary |work=The Guardian |access-date=2021-10-18 |date=2021-10-17 |archive-date=2021-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018071313/https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2021/oct/17/sir-david-amess-obituary |dead-url=no }}</ref>，政治兴趣就此萌发<ref name="Times obit" />，成年后更加入保守党<ref name="Guardian obit" />。埃默斯小时候有[[口吃|口吃]]的毛病，经[[言语治疗|言语治疗]]纠正后，天生的[[考克尼|考克尼]]口音完全丧失<ref name="Times obit" /><ref name="Tele obit" />。埃默斯之后就读于伯恩茅斯技术大学（今[[伯恩茅斯大学|伯恩茅斯大学]]科技系），获经济与政府理学士学位<ref name=ukwhoswho/><ref name="davidamess.co.uk">{{cite web|url=http://www.davidamess.co.uk/about-david|title=Profile|publisher=David Amess|access-date=9 May 2015|archive-date=2021-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018075110/https://www.davidamess.co.uk/about-david|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1970至1971年在[[貝思納爾綠地|貝思納爾綠地]]圣约翰浸信会小学教残障儿童，1974年至1976年任{{tsl|en|underwriter|承保人}}，后任招聘顾问<ref name="davidamess.co.uk"/><ref name="Guardian obit" />。

==政治生涯==
[[1979年英国大选|1979年英国大选]]，埃默斯争夺[[工党_(英国)|工党]]议员{{tsl|en|Arthur Lewis (British politician)|亚瑟·刘易斯}}在{{tsl|en|Newham North West (UK Parliament constituency)|西北纽汉 (英国国会选区)|西北纽汉选区}}的稳取席位。1982年，任[[紅橋區_(倫敦)|伦敦红桥区]]议员<ref>{{cite book |title=Dod's Parliamentary Companion 2004. |date=2003 |publisher=Vacher Dod |location=London |isbn=978-0-905702-43-8 |page=78 |edition=185th |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ja2IAAAAMAAJ&q=redbridge%2Bcouncillor%2Bamess |access-date=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017023642/https://books.google.com/books?id=ja2IAAAAMAAJ&q=redbridge%2Bcouncillor%2Bamess |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[1983年英国大选|1983年英国大选]]，时任{{tsl|en|Basildon (UK Parliament constituency)|巴西尔登 (英国国会选区)|巴西尔登选区}}保守党议员{{tsl|en|Harvey Proctor|哈维·普罗克特}}移到{{tsl|en|Billericay (UK Parliament constituency)|比勒里凯 (英国国会选区)|比勒里凯}}，埃默斯于1983年6月9日当选该区[[英国下议院|议员]]，接任他的职务<ref>{{cite web |title=Mr David Amess (Hansard) |url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/people/mr-david-amess/index.html |publisher=UK Parliament |access-date=2021-10-17 |archive-date=2020-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200924192241/https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/people/mr-david-amess/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃默斯举出{{tsl|en|Essex man|埃塞克斯人}}的新人口统计，证明当地人非常支持[[玛格丽特·撒切尔|玛格丽特·撒切尔]]政府。《{{tsl|en|Campaign (magazine)|政治活动 (杂志)|政治活动}}》称埃默斯是“新埃塞克斯人、工人阶级、电工父亲、右翼的代表，犹如锋利衣架，吵闹粗暴，不机敏”<ref>{{cite magazine |title=What sort of person signs up as an advertiser? |magazine=Campaign |date=1990-01-26}}</ref> 。

埃默斯兼任国会议员及地方议员，直至1986年卸任红桥区议员，专注于[[威斯敏斯特宫|威斯敏斯特宫]]的议席。[[1987年英國大選|1987年英國大選]]，凭借个人培养的大量追随者，以微弱优势保住议席。选后获任命为[[博文高|博文高]]的{{tsl|en|Parliamentary Private Secretary|国会私人秘书}}，随博文高的部长生涯做了10年。[[1992年英国大选|1992年英国大选]]再获连任，是保守派意外赢得此次选举的象征，其所在的巴西尔登选区是成败关键<ref>{{cite news |title=David Amess |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/2173294.stm |access-date=2021-10-15 |work=BBC News |date=2002-10-16 |archive-date=2004-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040205083628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/2173294.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[1997年英国大选|1997年英国大选]]前夕，巴西尔登选区被重新划分为两部分，纳入邻近选区。埃默斯认为{{tsl|en|Boundary commissions (United Kingdom)|边界委员会 (英国)|边界委员会}}在当地新增选区，“强奸了巴西尔登镇”<ref>{{cite work |last=Roth |first=Andrew |title=Parliamentary Profiles (Andrew Roth) |contribution=AMESS, David |year=2005 |publisher=Parliamentary Profile Services Ltd. |url=http://internetserver.bishopsgate.org.uk/Details/archive/110028694 |contribution-url=http://internetserver.bishopsgate.org.uk/files/Parliamentary%20Profiles%20Archive/A-D/AMESS,%20David/AMESS,%20David.pdf |via=the Bishopsgate Institute |accessdate=2021-10-15 |archive-date=2021-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041335/http://internetserver.bishopsgate.org.uk/Details/archive/110028694 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由于埃默斯的支持者仅占少数，新的巴西尔登选区确定会被工党夺取，埃默斯遂在其他选区竞逐连任，而他早在1995年6月就接任退休内阁大臣{{tsl|en|Paul Channon|保罗·香农}}的[[西紹森德_(英國國會選區)|西紹森德选区]]席位，1997年大选在此选区获胜，再度回归威斯敏斯特宫。同年，{{tsl|en|Angela Smith, Baroness Smith of Basildon|安吉拉·埃文斯·史密斯，巴西尔登史密斯男爵夫人|安吉拉·埃文斯·史密斯}}以1.3万多票，赢得新划分的巴西尔登选区<ref>{{cite web|title=Election Data 1997|url=http://www.electoralcalculus.co.uk/electdata_1997.txt|publisher={{tsl|en|Electoral Calculus||Electoral Calculus}}|accessdate=2015-10-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111015054424/http://www.electoralcalculus.co.uk/electdata_1997.txt|archivedate=2011-10-15|url-status=dead}}</ref>。

===西绍森德城市地位===
埃默斯长期在所属选区的主城镇[[濱海紹森德|濱海紹森德]]举行竞选活动<ref>{{cite news |last1=Webber |first1=Esther |title=UK MP David Amess dies after stabbing attack |url=https://www.politico.eu/article/uk-mp-david-amess-dies-in-stabbing-attack/ |work=Politico |date=2021-10-15 |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016183551/https://www.politico.eu/article/uk-mp-david-amess-dies-in-stabbing-attack/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Sir David Amess: Long-serving MP and city status campaigner |url=https://www.northern-times.co.uk/news/national/article/sir-david-amess-long-serving-mp-and-city-status-campaigner-31640/ |work=Northern Times |agency=PA News |date=2021-10-15 |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041335/https://www.northern-times.co.uk/news/national/article/sir-david-amess-long-serving-mp-and-city-status-campaigner-31640/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年10月18日，绍森德获[[英國城市地位|城市地位]]，以纪念遇害的埃默斯<ref>{{cite news |title=Sir David Amess: Southend to become a city in honour of MP |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-northamptonshire-58956615 |work=BBC News |date=2021-10-18 |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041339/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-england-northamptonshire-58956615 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Elgot |first1=Jessica |title=Southend to become city in honour of Sir David Amess |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/18/southend-to-become-city-in-honour-of-sir-david-amess |work=The Guardian |date=2021-10-18 |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041356/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/18/southend-to-become-city-in-honour-of-sir-david-amess |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===立法参与===
