埃默斯支持多项议会法案<ref>{{cite news |title=Candidate David Amess |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/vote2001/candidates/candidates/5/52901.stm |access-date=2021-10-17 |work=BBC News Vote2001 |archive-date=2016-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306000010/http://news.bbc.co.uk/hi/english/static/vote2001/candidates/candidates/5/52901.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括《1988年防止残酷束缚法》（''Protection Against Cruel Tethering Act 1988''）<ref>{{Cite legislation UK |type=act |year=1988 |chapter=31 |act=Protection against Cruel Tethering Act 1988 |section=1 |date= |accessdate=2015-05-09 |mode=cs1}}</ref>和《2000年家居供暖与节能法》（''Warm Homes and Energy Conservation Act 2000''）<ref>{{Cite legislation UK |type=act |year=2000 |chapter=31 |act=Warm Homes and Energy Conservation Act 2000 |section= |date= |accessdate=2015-05-09 |mode=cs1}}</ref> 。

