==== 1988年防止残酷束缚法 ====
《防止残酷束缚法》由长期支持动物福利的埃默斯提出，得到{{tsl|en|National Farmers' Union of England and Wales|英格兰和威尔士全国农民联盟|全国农民联盟}}支持。埃默斯在下议院表示这项{{tsl|en|Ten Minute Rule|十分钟规则}}法案源于“埃塞克斯马匹保护协会的提议”<ref>{{Cite Hansard |house=House of Commons |title=Active Citizenship |url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/1991/may/23/active-citizenship#S6CV0191P0_19910523_HOC_47 |date=1991-05-23 |column_start=1070 |column_end=1078 |accessdate=2015-05-09 }} {{Wayback|url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/1991/may/23/active-citizenship#S6CV0191P0_19910523_HOC_47 |date=20190626121251 }}</ref>。

====  2000年家居供暖与节能法 ====
[[File:David_Amess.jpg|thumb]]
埃默斯最广为人知的法案是《2000年家居供暖与节能法》。根据埃默斯在下议院的演讲，该法案在他被排除出指定议员投票（Private Members Ballot）后提出<ref name="hansard.millbanksystems.com">{{Cite Hansard |house=House of Commons |url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/2000/mar/10/warm-homes-and-energy-conservation-bill |date=2000-03-10 |title=Warm Homes and Energy Conservation Bill |column_start=1296 |column_end=1359 |access-date=2014-05-10 }} {{Wayback|url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/2000/mar/10/warm-homes-and-energy-conservation-bill |date=20201126134757 }}</ref>。后来他遇到[[地球之友|地球之友]]组织成员马丁·威廉姆斯（Martyn Williams），对方说选区内有位居民在寒冷的家中死去，让他认为需要通过该法<ref name="hansard.millbanksystems.com"/>。

法案要求内阁大臣“公布并实施一项减少燃料贫困的战略”<ref>{{Cite legislation UK |type=act |year=2000 |chapter=31 |act=Warm Homes and Energy Conservation Act 2000 |section= |date= |accessdate=2014-05-10 | quote = An Act to require the Secretary of State to publish and implement a strategy for reducing fuel poverty; to require the setting of targets for the implementation of that strategy; and for connected purposes. |mode=cs1}}</ref>，使得英国政府对燃料贫困的态度及政策产生重大转变<ref name="jrf.org.uk">{{cite journal |last=Stockton |first=Helen |display-authors=1 |author2=Ron Campbell |editor=National Energy Action |title=Time to reconsider UK energy and fuel poverty policies? |date=2011-10 |url=http://www.jrf.org.uk/sites/files/jrf/fuel-poverty-policy-summary.pdf |access-date=2014-05-10 |publisher=Joseph Rowntree Foundation |journal= |archive-date=2013-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228052419/http://www.jrf.org.uk/sites/files/jrf/fuel-poverty-policy-summary.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，燃料贫困户从1996年的510万户减少到2004年的120万户<ref name="jrf.org.uk"/>。

===议会委员会===
====健康专责委员会====
1998年至2007年，埃默斯任健康专责委员会委员。得益在委员会中的地位，他于1999年任保守党健康委员会后座议员<ref>{{cite web|title=David Amess MP|url=http://www.southendwestconservatives.com/david-amess-mp|publisher=Southend West Conservatives|access-date=2015-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103174852/http://www.southendwestconservatives.com/david-amess-mp|archive-date=2013-11-03|url-status=dead}}</ref>，自此开始关注多项健康议题。2004年，在埃默斯的极力推动下，英国[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]状况调查报告出炉<ref>{{cite report |authors=House of Commons Health Committee |date=2004-05-27 |title=Obesity |type=Third Report of Session 2003–04 |volume=I |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmselect/cmhealth/23/23.pdf |location=London |publisher=The Stationery Office Limited |page= |docket= |access-date=2014-05-10 |quote= |archive-date=2021-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210624095022/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm200304/cmselect/cmhealth/23/23.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。报告指三分之二的英国人超重或有肥胖问题，促使委员会进一步讨论肥胖问题成因，提出各项改善措施。埃默斯一直关注该问题，于2013年7月的[[首相答问环节|首相答问环节]]提出一系列相关问题<ref>{{Cite web|title=House of Commons Hansard Written Answers for 10 July 2013 (pt 0003)|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201314/cmhansrd/cm130710/text/130710w0003.htm#13071097002608|access-date=2021-10-16|publisher=UK Parliament|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709183507/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201314/cmhansrd/cm130710/text/130710w0003.htm#13071097002608|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

