===拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格===
埃默斯多年来提倡为在[[第二次世界大战期间的匈牙利|纳粹占领匈牙利]]期间拯救上万名犹太人而丢掉性命的瑞典外交官[[拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格|拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格]]设立纪念像。该项提议早在1980年代末的{{tsl|en|Question time|问答时间|议会问答大会}}上被提出<ref>{{Cite Hansard |house=House of Commons |title=Mr. Raoul Wallenberg |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm198889/cmhansrd/1989-01-27/Writtens-2.html#Writtens-2_sbhd8 |date=1989-01-27 |column=773 |access-date=2015-05-09 }} {{Wayback|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm198889/cmhansrd/1989-01-27/Writtens-2.html#Writtens-2_sbhd8 |date=20201204210604 }}</ref>，当时埃默斯提议为瓦伦贝格颁发英国荣誉公民。其后又在1989至90届议会尝试推动《拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格法案》通过<ref>{{Cite Hansard |house=House of Commons |title=Raoul Wallenberg (Memorial) |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm198990/cmhansrd/1990-01-08/Orals-2.html#Orals-2_dpthd3 |date=1990-01-08 |column=707 |access-date=2021-10-18 }} {{Wayback|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm198990/cmhansrd/1990-01-08/Orals-2.html#Orals-2_dpthd3 |date=20200920073626 }}</ref>，1996年为纪念瓦伦贝格举行休会期辩论<ref>{{Cite Hansard |house=House of Commons |title=Raoul Wallenberg |url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/1996/feb/26/raoul-wallenberg |date=1996-02-26 |column_start=695 |column_end=702 |access-date=2021-10-18 }} {{Wayback|url=https://api.parliament.uk/historic-hansard/commons/1996/feb/26/raoul-wallenberg |date=20211019205439 }}</ref>。1997年，由雕塑家{{tsl|en|Philip Jackson (sculptor)|菲利普·杰克逊}}打造的{{tsl|en|Raoul Wallenberg Monument, London|伦敦拉乌尔·瓦伦贝格纪念像|纪念像}}在伦敦{{tsl|en|Western Marble Arch Synagogue|西部大理石拱门犹太教堂}}外的{{tsl|en|Great Cumberland Place|大坎伯兰广场}}揭幕<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/memorial-to-wallenberg-1.47176|title=Memorial to Wallenberg|date=1997-02-27|newspaper=The Irish Times|access-date=2021-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041402/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/memorial-to-wallenberg-1.47176|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

