===《黄铜眼》===
埃默斯亮相时事恶搞电视节目《{{tsl|en|Brass Eye|黄铜眼}}》，在别人的糊弄下拍了一段广告，以夸张口吻告诫人们小心所谓的东欧毒品“蛋糕”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/shortcuts/2015/oct/23/david-amess-from-chris-morris-and-cake-to-scrutinising-drugs-policy|title=David Amess: from Chris Morris and 'cake' to scrutinising drugs policy|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2021-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018090013/https://www.theguardian.com/society/shortcuts/2015/oct/23/david-amess-from-chris-morris-and-cake-to-scrutinising-drugs-policy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默斯后来在议员就“蛋糕”及真实存在的[[巧茶|巧茶]]和[[Γ-羟基丁酸|Γ-羟基丁酸]]提问。对此，内政部长错误称“蛋糕”是毒品{{tsl|en|3,4-methylenedioxy-N-benzylamphetamine|3,4-亚甲二氧基-N-苄基苯丙胺}}的绰号<ref>{{cite web |author=Department of the Official Report (Hansard), House of Commons, Westminster |url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm199596/cmhansrd/vo960723/text/60723w10.htm#60723w10.html_wqn10 |title=House of Commons Hansard Written Answers for 23 Jul 1996 (pt 10) |publisher=Publications.parliament.uk |access-date=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230202706/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm199596/cmhansrd/vo960723/text/60723w10.htm#60723w10.html_wqn10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2001年，《黄铜眼》将这段广告收录进DVD，并应埃默斯的要求加入免责声明，强调他不赞同使用娱乐性毒品<ref>{{cite AV media |date=2002 |title=Brass Eye series and special |medium=DVD |publisher=Channel 4/2 Entertain |asin=B000066NT9 |time=24:07 in "Drugs episode"}}</ref>。

==政治观点==
[[File:Official_portrait_of_Sir_David_Amess_crop_2.jpg|thumb]]
埃默斯在下议院投票时一般会跟随保守党的政策<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.publicwhip.org.uk/mp.php?mpn=David_Amess&mpc=Southend_West|title=Voting Record – David Amess MP, Southend West (10009) – The Public Whip|publisher=Publicwhip.org.uk|access-date=2015-05-09|archive-date=2017-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014135757/http://www.publicwhip.org.uk/mp.php?mpn=David_Amess&mpc=Southend_West|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Primary source-inline}}。他投票赞同{{tsl|en|2003 invasion of Iraq|2003年进攻伊拉克}}，但事后批评工党政府没有找出将行动合理化的[[大规模杀伤性武器|大规模杀伤性武器]]。外交政策方面，他是{{tsl|en|Conservative Friends of Israel|保守党以色列之友}}领导成员。他是少数几位支持{{tsl|en|Parliamentary motion to impeach Tony Blair|弹劾托尼·布莱尔的议会动议|弹劾托尼·布莱尔}}的保守党议员<ref>{{Cite news|date=2016-05-16|title=New move to put Tony Blair on trial over Iraq War gains cross-party support|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/tony-blair-iraq-war-chilcot-inquiry-report-alex-salmond-move-to-impeach-a7031766.html|access-date=2021-10-15|work=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016134943/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/tony-blair-iraq-war-chilcot-inquiry-report-alex-salmond-move-to-impeach-a7031766.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年8月，埃默斯与30名保守党员投票反对对叙利亚发动军事行动。他后来说自己和同事们的投票立场之所以不同，是觉得如果以前投票反对向伊拉克发动战争，伊拉克的情况可能会完全不同<ref>{{Cite web|title=House of Commons Hansard Debates for 19 Dec 2013 (pt 0002)|url=https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201314/cmhansrd/cm131219/debtext/131219-0002.htm#131219-0002.htm_spnew85|access-date=2021-10-16|website=publications.parliament.uk|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020645/https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201314/cmhansrd/cm131219/debtext/131219-0002.htm#131219-0002.htm_spnew85|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默斯支持恢复{{tsl|en|Capital punishment in the United Kingdom|英国死刑制度|死刑}}<ref name="bbc_profile">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/2173294.stm|title=David Amess|date=2002-10-16|access-date=2008-05-05|work=BBC News|archive-date=2004-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040205083628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk_politics/2173294.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他批评[[伊朗|伊朗]]政府，支持[[伊朗反抗力量全國議會|伊朗反抗力量全國議會]]，公开为{{tsl|en|Maryam Rajavi|玛丽亚姆·拉贾维}}的10点宣言背书<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mess|first1=David|title=Don't Ignore Iran|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/realspin/2016/07/06/iran-extremism-consequences/|work=Forbes|date=2016-07-06|access-date=2016-07-24|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015225324/https://www.forbes.com/sites/realspin/2016/07/06/iran-extremism-consequences/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Lo|first1=Joe|title=UK MPs attend rally for Iranian group whose leader is still banned by London|url=https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/uk-mps-attended-rally-iranian-group-whose-leader-still-banned-london|work={{tsl|en|Middle East Eye||Middle East Eye}}|date=2018-01-30|access-date=2021-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020606/https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/uk-mps-attended-rally-iranian-group-whose-leader-still-banned-london|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默斯支持难民和寻求庇护者<ref>{{cite news |title=Church minister leads on Our Turn Campaign for child refugees in Southend-on-Sea |url=https://www.lrbc.org.uk/news/2019/07/01/church-minister-leads-on-our-turn-campaign-for-child-refugees-in-southend-on-sea/ |access-date=2021-10-17 |publisher=Leigh Road Baptist Church |date=2019-07-01 |archive-date=2020-08-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813194154/https://www.lrbc.org.uk/news/2019/07/01/church-minister-leads-on-our-turn-campaign-for-child-refugees-in-southend-on-sea/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Desouza |first1=Danielle |title=Asylum seeker pays tribute to ‘supportive’ and ‘welcoming’ Sir David Amess |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/home-office-asylum-seeker-southendonsea-ucl-theresa-may-b960832.html |access-date=2021-10-17 |work=Evening Standard |date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2021-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211018083508/https://www.standard.co.uk/news/uk/home-office-asylum-seeker-southendonsea-ucl-theresa-may-b960832.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

埃默斯反对堕胎。2005年6月，埃默斯支持[[勞倫斯·羅伯森|勞倫斯·羅伯森]]提出的《禁止堕胎（英格兰和威尔士）法案》（Prohibition of Abortion (England and Wales) Bill），该法案几乎完全禁止堕胎<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amess claims figures will help win anti-abortion vote|url=https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/local_news/2155320.amess-claims-figures-will-help-win-anti-abortion-vote/|access-date=2021-10-15|website=Echo|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020648/https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/local_news/2155320.amess-claims-figures-will-help-win-anti-abortion-vote/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=MP's delight at knighthood for his long career|url=https://www.braintreeandwithamtimes.co.uk/news/south_essex_news/11699365.mp-david-amess-delight-at-knighthood-for-his-long-career/|access-date=2021-10-15|website=Braintree and Witham Times|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041339/https://www.braintreeandwithamtimes.co.uk/news/south_essex_news/11699365.mp-david-amess-delight-at-knighthood-for-his-long-career/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。进入下议院后，埃默斯通常情况下反对推动[[英國LGBT權益|LGBT权利]]，包括反对平等{{tsl|en|Age of consent reform in the United Kingdom|英国同意年龄改革|同意年龄}}改革及[[英国同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]<ref>{{cite news |author=<!--Staff writer(s)/no by-line.--> |date=2013-02-05 |title=MP-by-MP: Gay marriage vote |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-21346694.amp |work=BBC News |access-date=2021-10-15 |archive-date=2021-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020643/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-21346694.amp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Baynes |first=Chris |date=2019-07-10 |title=All the MPs who voted against lifting abortion ban and same-sex marriage in Northern Ireland |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/same-sex-marriage-northern-ireland-list-every-mp-voted-against-lifting-abortion-ban-a8998456.html |work=The Independent |access-date=2021-10-15 |archive-date=2021-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020606/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/same-sex-marriage-northern-ireland-list-every-mp-voted-against-lifting-abortion-ban-a8998456.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

埃默斯主张改善[[动物福利|动物福利]]及[[畜牧业|畜牧业]]。他从头到尾投票支持{{tsl|en|Legislation on hunting with dogs|对狩猎犬只的立法|禁止猎狐活动}}及{{tsl|en|hare coursing|追猎野兔}}，是保守党动物福利基金会（Conservative Animal Welfare Foundation）的赞助人<ref>{{Cite web|title=About Us|url=https://www.conservativeanimalwelfarefoundation.org/about/|access-date=2021-10-15|website=Conservative Animal Welfare Foundation|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020606/https://www.conservativeanimalwelfarefoundation.org/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还支持禁止用笼困住野鸟、动物试验、养殖走私幼犬、停止运输出口活体动物<ref>{{Cite web|title=BANNING BATTERY CAGES FOR GAMEBIRDS - Early Day Motions - UK Parliament|url=https://edm.parliament.uk/early-day-motion/40080/banning-battery-cages-for-gamebirds|access-date=2021-10-15|website=edm.parliament.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211020041337/https://edm.parliament.uk/early-day-motion/40080/banning-battery-cages-for-gamebirds|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Leigh: MP takes stand on animal testing |url=https://www.leightimes.co.uk/article.cfm?id=128721&headline=Leigh:%20MP%20takes%20stand%20on%20animal%20testing&sectionIs=news&searchyear=2021 |access-date=2021-10-16 |work=Leigh Times |date=2021-04-21 |archive-date=2021-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211019194625/https://www.leightimes.co.uk/article.cfm?id=128721&headline=Leigh:%20MP%20takes%20stand%20on%20animal%20testing&sectionIs=news&searchyear=2021 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=David Amess speaks in the Puppy Farms debate|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=spQq84Q9FrY|language=en|access-date=2021-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020643/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=spQq84Q9FrY|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-06-16|title=Tory and Labour MPs condemn new delay on live animal export ban|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/live-exports-ban-delay-uk-eu-defra-david-amess-a9569366.html|access-date=2021-10-15|website=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020643/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/home-news/live-exports-ban-delay-uk-eu-defra-david-amess-a9569366.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Campaigners join Joanna Lumley in international demonstration to #StopLiveTransport|url=https://www.ciwf.org.uk/media/press-releases-statements/2018/06/campaigners-join-joanna-lumley-and-compassion-in-world-farming-in-international-demonstration-to-stoplivetransport|access-date=2021-10-15|website=www.ciwf.org.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020606/https://www.ciwf.org.uk/media/press-releases-statements/2018/06/campaigners-join-joanna-lumley-and-compassion-in-world-farming-in-international-demonstration-to-stoplivetransport|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2011年9月，埃默斯指责[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]在报道[[以色列|以色列]]的事件时待有偏见，画面“被非常不成比例地覆盖住”，显得当地“灯光昏暗”<ref>{{Cite news|date=2011-09-07|title=Conservative MP David Amess attacks BBC pay and 'bias'|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-14830938|access-date=2021-10-17|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017035526/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-14830938|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

埃默斯坚定的[[歐洲懷疑主義|欧洲怀疑主义者]]，在[[英國去留歐盟公投|英國去留歐盟公投]]前便公开支持[[英國脫歐|英國脫歐]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-35616946 |title=EU vote: Where the cabinet and other MPs stand |publisher=BBC |date=2016-06-22 |access-date=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2020-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515051923/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-eu-referendum-35616946 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="thespectatorwhichtorympsbackbrexit">{{cite news|last1=Goodenough|first1=Tom|title=Which Tory MPs back Brexit, who doesn't and who is still on the fence?|url=http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2016/02/which-tory-mps-back-brexit-who-doesnt-and-who-is-still-on-the-fence/|access-date=2016-10-11|work=The Spectator|date=2016-02-16|archive-date=2017-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170203120144/http://blogs.spectator.co.uk/2016/02/which-tory-mps-back-brexit-who-doesnt-and-who-is-still-on-the-fence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，指投票留下来是非常危险的大错误，认为“议会主权丧失”是[[英欧关系|英欧关系]]的最大负面影响<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/sir-david-explains-why-he-backing-brexit |title=Sir David explains why he is backing Brexit |publisher=UK Parliament |date=2016-06-17 |access-date=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016020604/https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/sir-david-explains-why-he-backing-brexit |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃默斯批评时任美国总统[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]在与[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]会面时干涉[[英國去留歐盟公投|英國去留歐盟公投]]，说奥巴马“根本没有干涉的权利”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/14450777.Southend_MP_warns_Obama__Stay_out_of_British_politics/ |title=Southend MP Sir David Amess warns Barack Obama: Stay out of British politics |publisher=The Echo (Essex) |date=2016-04-25 |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2018-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118215542/https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/14450777.Southend_MP_warns_Obama__Stay_out_of_British_politics/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==荣誉==
埃默斯在{{tsl|en|2015 New Year Honours|2015年新年授勋}}中获封[[下級勳位爵士|下級勳位爵士]]<ref>{{London Gazette|issue=61092 |supp=y|page=N2|date=2014-12-31}}</ref>。他是{{tsl|en|Imperial Society of Knights Bachelor|帝国骑士学会学士}}{{citation needed|date=October 2021}}。

在2011年{{tsl|en|Dods Group|Dods Group|Dods}}慈善冠军奖（Charity Champion Awards）上获得动物福利和环保冠军（Animal Welfare and Environment Champion），由[[下議院議長_(英國)|下议院议长]][[约翰·伯科_(英国)|约翰·伯科]]在议长府国事厅颁奖，以表彰他动物福利方面的领导地位及承诺<ref name="wspa.org.uk">{{cite web |url=http://www.wspa.org.uk/latestnews/2011/David_Amess_MP.aspx |title=News | UK World Animal Protection |publisher=Wspa.org.uk |access-date=2015-05-09 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307010827/http://www.wspa.org.uk/latestnews/2011/David_Amess_MP.aspx |archive-date=2014-03-07}}</ref>。该奖项授予在解决动物福利和自然环境问题方面做出最大努力的议员<ref name="wspa.org.uk"/>。

在2012年由Dods举办的议会慈善冠军招待会上，埃默斯获“终身成就奖”，表彰他对慈善事业作出的终身承诺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/charity-champion-david-amess-mp-receives-outstanding-achievement-award-dods |title=A Charity Champion: David Amess MP Receives an Outstanding Achievement Award from Dods |publisher=Davidamess.co.uk |date=2012-06-28 |access-date=2015-05-09 |archive-date=2021-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015223308/https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/charity-champion-david-amess-mp-receives-outstanding-achievement-award-dods |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年获{{tsl|en|Grassroot Diplomat|草根外交官}}奖“保护动物权利政策驱动者”提名，表彰他长久以来对动物权利的贡献<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.grassrootdiplomat.org/news/2014/9/23/animal-lover-david-amess-mp-nominated-for-initiative-award |title=Animal Activist David Amess MP Nominated for Initiative Award – Grassroot Diplomat |publisher=Grassrootdiplomat.org |access-date=2015-05-09 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022012905/http://www.grassrootdiplomat.org/news/2014/9/23/animal-lover-david-amess-mp-nominated-for-initiative-award |archive-date=2014-10-22 }}</ref>。

==个人生活==
埃默斯与妻子朱丽娅·阿诺德有一个儿子和四个女儿。朱丽娅是丈夫的兼职个案工作者<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wilkinson|first1=Michael|last2=Hope|first2=Christopher|title=One in five MPs employs a family member: the full list revealed|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/mps-expenses/11706561/One-in-four-MPs-employs-a-family-member-the-full-list-revealed.html|work=Daily Telegraph|date=2015-06-29|accessdate=2021-10-18|archive-date=2017-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170402065627/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/mps-expenses/11706561/One-in-four-MPs-employs-a-family-member-the-full-list-revealed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儿子小大卫（David Jr.）2005年在夜店朝一名男子的头砸了一个[[香槟酒|香槟酒]]瓶，犯[[严重身体伤害|严重身体伤害]]罪，入狱四年<ref>{{cite news |title=MP's son jailed for bottle attack |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/essex/4267591.stm |access-date=2020-10-25 |work=BBC News |date=2005-02-15 |archive-date=2022-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204151941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/essex/4267591.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。二女{{tsl|en|Katie Amess|凯蒂·埃默斯|凯蒂}}是演员<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/local_news/9682394.MP___s_daughter_Katie_Amess_is_now_a_Hollywood_starlet|title=MP's daughter Katie Amess is now a Hollywood starlet|newspaper=Basildon Echo|date=2012-05-03|access-date=2021-10-15|archive-date=2018-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180815024314/http://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/local_news/9682394.MP___s_daughter_Katie_Amess_is_now_a_Hollywood_starlet/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃默斯是[[英超联赛|英超联赛]]球队[[西汉姆联|西汉姆联]]的忠实拥趸，2016年5月在[[博林球场|博林球场]]观看球队决赛<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/sir-david-reflects-west-ham-united%E2%80%99s-memorable-final-game-boleyn-ground|title=SIR DAVID REFLECTS ON WEST HAM UNITED’S MEMORABLE FINAL GAME AT THE BOLEYN GROUND|website=David Amess|access-date=2021-10-18|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016120347/https://www.davidamess.co.uk/news/sir-david-reflects-west-ham-united%E2%80%99s-memorable-final-game-boleyn-ground|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

身为爱动物人士，埃默斯一家有多只宠物。2016年，一家人收养获救的[[巴哥犬|巴哥犬]]莉莉（Lily）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sir David Amess MP awarded Cruelty Free International MP of the month|publisher=Cruelty Free International|url=https://www.crueltyfreeinternational.org/what-we-do/blog/sir-david-amess-mp-awarded-cruelty-free-international-mp-month|access-date=2021-10-15|website=crueltyfreeinternational.org|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815111515/https://crueltyfreeinternational.org/what-we-do/blog/sir-david-amess-mp-awarded-cruelty-free-international-mp-month|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年，法国斗牛犬薇薇安（Vivienne）接替莉莉，参加威斯敏斯特年度犬展（Westminster Dog of the Year Show）<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/19615403.david-amess-running-westminster-dog-year-show/ |date=2021-09-30 |title=David Amess running in Westminster Dog of the Year Show |author=Lewis Berril |newspaper=Southend Echo |accessdate=2021-10-18 |archive-date=2021-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015221906/https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/19615403.david-amess-running-westminster-dog-year-show/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

埃默斯是地方慈善团体音乐人协会（The Music Man Society）的主席，该协会为有学习障碍的人提供音乐机会。他曾和协会成员出席在[[皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳|皇家阿爾伯特音樂廳]]和[[伦敦守护神剧院|伦敦守护神剧院]]的表演<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hurynag |first1=Ashna |title=Sir David Amess: Locals remember the 'always smiling, always energetic' MP who always had time for others |url=https://news.sky.com/story/sir-david-amess-locals-remember-the-always-smiling-always-energetic-mp-who-always-had-time-for-others-12435732 |access-date=2021-10-16 |publisher=Sky News |date=2021-10-16 |archive-date=2021-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017155028/https://news.sky.com/story/sir-david-amess-locals-remember-the-always-smiling-always-energetic-mp-who-always-had-time-for-others-12435732 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 遇害 ==
{{Main|大卫·埃默斯遇刺事件}}
2021年10月15日，埃默斯在[[滨海利|滨海利]]贝尔费尔斯卫理公会教堂（Belfairs Methodist Church）出席[[政治診療室|政治診療室]]活动时身中数刀<ref>{{Cite news|last=Emes|first=Toby|date=2021-10-15|title=MP Sir David Amess 'stabbed multiple times' at residents' surgery in Leigh|url=https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/19650476.sir-david-amess-mp-stabbed-leigh-church/|url-status=no|access-date=2021-10-15|website=Echo|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015140928/https://www.echo-news.co.uk/news/19650476.sir-david-amess-mp-stabbed-leigh-church/}}</ref>，当场伤重不治<ref>{{Cite web|title=Conservative MP Sir David Amess stabbed multiple times in incident at constituency surgery|url=https://news.sky.com/story/conservative-mp-david-amess-stabbed-multiple-times-in-incident-at-constituency-surgery-12434498|access-date=2021-10-15|website=Sky News|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017043501/https://news.sky.com/story/conservative-mp-david-amess-stabbed-multiple-times-in-incident-at-constituency-surgery-12434498|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Walker|first=Peter|date=2021-10-15|title=Conservative MP David Amess stabbed in Essex attack.|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/15/conservative-mp-peter-amess-stabbed-in-essex-attack|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211015130033/https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2021/oct/15/conservative-mp-david-amess-stabbed-in-essex-attack|archive-date=2021-10-15|access-date=2021-10-15|website=The Guardian}}</ref>。[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]宣布事件为“恐怖主义行为”<ref>{{Cite news|date=2021-10-15|title=Sir David Amess killing was terrorist incident, say police|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-58935372|access-date=2021-10-15|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017185831/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-58935372|dead-url=no}}</ref>，调查行动由苏格兰场反恐指挥部（Scotland Yard's Counter Terrorism Command），调查“与伊斯兰极端主义有关的潜在动机”<ref>{{Cite news|title=Ali Harbi Ali named as terror suspect in Sir David Amess murder|work=The National|url=https://www.thenationalnews.com/world/uk-news/2021/10/16/ali-harbi-ali-named-as-terror-suspect-in-sir-david-amess-murder/|access-date=2021-10-17|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017073306/https://www.thenationalnews.com/world/uk-news/2021/10/16/ali-harbi-ali-named-as-terror-suspect-in-sir-david-amess-murder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当局确认嫌犯为索马里裔英国公民阿里·哈比·阿里，依《恐怖主义法》将其扣留<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/uk-mps-killer-was-referred-to-counter-terrorism-scheme-reports|title=British MP's killer was referred to counter-terrorism scheme: Reports|website=The Straits Times (Singapore)|date=2021-10-17|access-date=2021-10-17|archive-date=2021-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017193909/https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/uk-mps-killer-was-referred-to-counter-terrorism-scheme-reports|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

